match A or B
=============================
egrep -h "christian|chapman"



match from christian to end
=============================
grep -Po "christian.*"

match from christian to bad
==========================
grep -Po "christian.*(?=bad)"

grep around a file
====================
grep -B 4
grep -A 4

cut 
=======
cut -c -100     <<< cut from 0 to 100 of line 



ls
===
show human readable file size
ls -lh
